HEADWORD: Ogham
<hw>Og"ham</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Ir.]</ety> <def>A
particular kind of writing practiced by the ancient Irish, and found in
inscriptions on stones, metals, etc.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>ogam</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
